## Quick Start

### 1. Configure Program

Edit `program_config.yaml` with program-specific settings.

### 2. Establish Baseline

```bash
# Create initial functional baseline
aerospacemodel baseline create \
  --type FBL \
  --name "{{ model_code }}-Initial" \
  --description "Initial program baseline"
```

### 3. Define Contracts

Create transformation contracts in `ASIT/CONTRACTS/active/`:

```bash
# Generate contract from template
aerospacemodel contract create \
  --template KITDM-CTR-LM-CSDB \
  --scope "ATA 21-28" \
  --output ASIT/CONTRACTS/active/
```

### 4. Run Transformation

```bash
# Execute under contract
aerospacemodel run \
  --contract {{ model_code }}-CTR-AMM-001 \
  --baseline FBL-{{ created_date[:4] }}-001
```

